caption.body: #OnThisDay in 2015, the last branded US Airways flight departed from Philadelphia International Airport and landed at San Francisco International Airport as American Airlines Flight 1939 (for the year the airline was established as All American Aviation). US Airways merged with American Airlines in 2013. Did you ever fly on US Airways?  Image: US Airways, Airbus A319, San Francisco International Airport (SFO), 2000. Gift of the William Hough Collection. 2017.095.006
